s); no by-line.-->|title=29 \u039c\u03b1\u03ca\u03bf\u03c5 1453: \u038c\u03c4\u03b1\u03bd \"\u03b7 \u03a0\u03cc\u03bb\u03b9\u03c2 \u03b5\u03ac\u03bb\u03c9....|trans-title=29 May 1453: When the City Fell...|language=el|date=29 May 2012|access-date=5 June 2017|url=http://www.iefimerida.gr/news/52795/29-%CE%BC%CE%B1%CF%8A%CE%BF%CF%85-1453-%CF%8C%CF%84%CE%B1%CE%BD-%C2%AB%CE%B7-%CF%80%CF%8C%CE%BB%CE%B9%CF%82-%CE%B5%CE%AC%CE%BB%CF%89%C2%BB|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170525102233/http://www.iefimerida.gr/news/52795/29-%CE%BC%CE%B1%CF%8A%CE%BF%CF%85-1453-%CF%8C%CF%84%CE%B1%CE%BD-%C2%AB%CE%B7-%CF%80%CF%8C%CE%BB%CE%B9%CF%82-%CE%B5%CE%AC%CE%BB%CF%89%C2%BB|archive-date=25 May 2017|url-status=live}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"vasilievhistbyz2\">{{cite book|author-first=Alexander|author-last=Vasiliev|translator-first=S.|translator-last=Ragozin|title=A History of the Byzantine Empire, Vol. II|volume=II|publisher=University of Wisconsin Press|location=Madison|date=1928}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"attidella10\">{{cite book|author-first=C.|author-last=Desimoni|title=Adamo di Montaldo|series=Atti della Societ\u00e0 Ligure di Storia Patria (Proceedings of the Ligurian Society for Homeland History)|volume=X|language=it|location=Genoa|year=1874}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"histbyzoxon\">{{cite book|last=Reinert|first=Stephen|title=The Oxford History of Byzantium|location=New York|publisher= Oxford UP|year=2002}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"norwichdeclinefall\">{{cite book | last = Norwich | first = John Julius | authorlink = John Julius Norwich | year = 1995 | title = Byzantium: The Decline and Fall | publisher = Alfred A. Knopf | location = New York | isbn = 0-679-41650-1}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Byzantines in Renaissance Italy\">{{Cite web |url=http://www.the-orb.net/encyclop/late/laterbyz/harris-ren.html |title=Byzantines in Renaissance Italy |access-date=10 April 2007 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20030930225420/http://www.the-orb.net/encyclop/late/laterbyz/harris-ren.html |archive-date=30 Sep